Sustainable Pharmaceutical Packaging Market Research, Consumer Behavior, Demand and Forecast
According to forecasts, the global sustainable pharmaceutical packaging market will grow from USD 92 billion in 2024 to USD 372.19 billion by 2034, with an expected CAGR of 15%. In 2024, North America led the sustainable pharmaceutical packaging market, with bottles, primary packaging, plastic materials, and oral drug applications dominating. Asia Pacific is projected to see the fastest growth during the forecast period.
